Question: Amount of alcohol excise tax by beverage type (wine)
Amount of alcohol excise tax by beverage type (wine)
DatavalueFootnote: State directly controlled the sale of (beer/wine/distilled spirits) at the retail and/or wholesale levels. State prices for (beer/wine/distilled spirits) combined both markups and taxes, so tax rates for this beverage type could not be determined.
